author: jaro-sevcik
message:
PR #30810: [XLA:GPU] Expose syevBatched from cusolver

Imported from GitHub PR https://github.com/openxla/xla/pull/30810

This exposes syevBatched* functions from cusolver to be
usable by JAX. We need the batched version to speed up
jax.lax.linalg.eigh for non-trivial batch sizes.

See https://github.com/jax-ml/jax/issues/31368
Copybara import of the project:

--
6854251d566aaf57de939d94447f251f4aaea4a9 by Jaroslav Sevcik <jsevcik@nvidia.com>:

[gpu] Expose syevBatched from cusolver

Merging this change closes #30810

PiperOrigin-RevId: 802458964
